@prefix dct:    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> .
@prefix rdf:    <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> .
@prefix skos:   <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#> .
@prefix rdfs:   <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix schema:	<https://schema.org/>.
@prefix proctypes: <http://purl.org/procurement/public-contracts-procedure-types#> .
@prefix :       <http://purl.org/map4scrutiny-values#>.


#   These terms are all described and designated in Portuguese. 
#   This decision was made due to the high complexity in translating 
#   legal documents and not finding an official version. 
#   The Property Regimen is the only Scheme with an english label 
#   because a document from a legal firm was found. 

